title: paintingAwarenessSuccess
---
[nomarkup][The vibrantly colored soup of mismatched geometric shapes is nauseating, but you manage to see past that. You reach up to dislodge the panels in the polyptych. Applying a modest amount of force to the largest painting in the center unlatches it, revealing a paper stamp on it's back.][/nomarkup] #success
-> Continue
{$kieran}: Did you find something?
-> {$pcName}: I'm not sure. Call it a gut feeling.
    <<if (GetCompanionInfluence($kieran) >4) or ($toldKieranAboutVision ==true)>>
    {$kieran}: I'll leave you to it then. If it's instinct it's probably important. \[He looks at the painting with curiosity\]
        <<if GetIsPartyMemberRecruited($anastasia) is true>>
            {$anastasia}: My, our nerd is giving up to gut feelings. Something happened when I wasn't looking?
        <<endif>>
    <<else>>
    {$kieran}: I hope it's something important, not just "I've got a feeling". We don't have time for art admiration.
    -> Continue
        <<if GetIsPartyMemberRecruited($anastasia) is true>>
            {$anastasia}: It's not even that pretty to look at. \[She cocks her head to the side like she'd like to see the canvas in another direction.\]
        <<endif>>
    <<endif>>
    <<jump paintingSuccessExamination>>
