title: paintingWitsSuccess
---
[nomarkup][This painting is here on purpose. It's not a simple wall decoration. It's here for a reason. It just doesn't sit with Diana proudly painting herself as a british punk rocker. Otherwise she’d just place Sex Pistols or The Exploited posters on the wall. Maybe there’s something worth looking for behind one part of this poliptich? You go with your gut, and dislodge one of the paintings. You were right. There's a paper stamp on the back.][/nomarkup] #success
{$kieran}: Did you find something?
    -> {$pcName}: I'm not sure. But those paintings don't fit in here.
        {$kieran}: \[He gently scratches his chin thinking\] Hm… you're right. I would've placed those rather in some kind of CEO's office or gallery. Not in the punk rocker hideout.
        <<if GetIsPartyMemberRecruited($anastasia) is true>>
        {$anastasia}: Maybe it has some sentimental value? Because it certainly doesn't have any aesthetic one.
        <<endif>>
        <<jump paintingSuccessExamination>>
